All Classes

Class Description
Basic
Basic contains methods to make the most simple and common html elements.
Build
Build contains more advanced methods that allow you to make more complex html/css creations, but can be more difficult to use.
Container
Container has methods to make some of the most common container-type elements.
Controller
Used as a reference point by all classes to access the data
Data
Data contains the variables that handle and store the html/css information.
Image
Image contains methods that allow you to add images to your html page.
Link
Link contains a single method that allow you to make a standard html link element.
List
List contains methods that allow you to make a variety of html list elements.
Style
Style contains all of the css/styling methods.
Table
Table contains a method that allows users to make a basic html table.
Write
Write has methods that allow you to finalize your content, and write your html/css to their respective pages.
